<div class="modal fade" id="aboutModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="aboutModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog model-lg" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title" id="aboutModalLabel">Modal title</h5>
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                    <span class="close-btn" aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
              <div class="app-card-container">


                  <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                    
                     <div class="profile-pic">
                       <%= image_tag 'Profile.JPG', width: 200, class: 'image-shadow' %>
                     </div>

                      <div class="skills">
                        <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
                          
                        <div class="skill">
                          <h5><%= skill.title %></h5>
                            
                            <div class="progress">
                              <div 
                                class="progress-bar bg-warning"
                                role="progressbar"
                                aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                                aria-valuemax="100"
                                style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                              >
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>

                        <% end %>
                      </div>

                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-9">

                      <h1 class="overview-text">Overview</h1>

                      <p> I am driven by building highly intuitive web applications with a strong focus on user experience and design. I specialize in a full-stack Ruby on Rails development environment.  With a college background in the arts and music, I also bring a keen design sensibility to every project.
                      </p>

                      <p>I am the creator of the website <%= link_to "AuditionCafe.com", "https://AuditionCafe.com" %>, a classical music job board that simplifies the process of finding and posting music auditions. I am also the founder/director of <%= link_to "MusAid.org", "http://musaid.org" %>, a 501(c)3 non-profit that supports musical institutions around the world through educational exchanges.
                      </p>

                      <p>
                       I was born in Thailand and have spent the majority of my life living overseas in Vietnam, Laos, India, Kyrgyzstan and Romania.  I am currently based in beautiful Miami Beach, Florida.</p>
                      
                      <p>
                        <button
                          class='btn btn-primary about-btn'
                          type='button'
                          data-toggle='collapse'
                          data-target='#education'
                          aria-expanded='false'
                          aria-controler='education'
                        >
                  
                        Education
                        </button>

                        <button
                          class='btn btn-primary about-btn'
                          type='button'
                          data-toggle='collapse'
                          data-target='#bio'
                          aria-expanded='false'
                          aria-controler='bio'
                        >
                        
                        Bio Information
                        </button>

                        <button class="btn btn-primary about-btn">
                          <%= link_to "Linked In", "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kevin-schaffter", target: :_blank %>
                        </button>

                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-flat float-right" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>

                      </p>

                      <p>
                        <div class="collapse" id="bio">
                          <div class="card card-block">
                            <p><span>Citizenship:</span> American, Canadian &amp; Thai 
                            </p>

                            <br>

                            <p><span>Place of birth:</span> Bangkok, Thailand
                            </p>

                            <br>

                            <p><span>Countries where lived:</span> Thailand (1989-1993), Vietnam (1993-1996), Romania (1996-2002), India (2002-2005), USA (2005-Present)
                            </p>

                            <br>

                            <p><span>Languages:</span> English &amp; Spanish</p>
                         

                            <br>

                            <p><span>Travel:</span> Argentina, Belize, Bolivia, Bulgaria, Cambodia, Canada, China &amp; Hong Kong, Colombia, Cyprus, Czech Republic, Egypt, El Salvador, France, Germany, Guatemala, Haiti, Italy, India, Ireland, Israel, Kyrgyzstan, Laos, Latvia, Malaysia, The Netherlands, Nicaragua, Norway, Palestine, Peru, The Philippines, Portugal, Romania, Spain, Sri Lanka, Switzerland, Taiwan, Thailand, Turkey, United Kingdom, United States of America, Uruguay and Vietnam.
                            </p>

                          </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="collapse" id="education">
                          <div class="card card-block">
                            <p><span><%= image_tag 'yale_logo.png', width: 22, class: 'school-logo' %>Yale University</span> - MMus</p>
                          </div>

                          <div class="card card-block">
                            <p><span><%= image_tag 'indiana_logo.png', width: 22, class: 'school-logo' %>Indiana University</span> - BMus</p>
                          </div>

                          <div class="card card-block">
                           <span class="courses"> Courses </span>
                            <div>Learn Ruby the Hard Way - Zed A. Shaw</div>
                            <div>Disecting Ruby on Rails - DevCamp</div>
                          </div>

                        </div>
                      </div>       
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>
</div>

